709165f-a.text:
1020 Fifth Ave., at the N.E. corner of East 83rd Street. Also shown is East 83rd Street, at, adjoining and east of the afore said corner. Note the 2-story frame house (No. 3 East 83rd Street), adjoining the newly completed co-operative apartment house.
Spring 1925.

709166f-a.text:
1020-1027 Fifth Ave., east side, from 83rd, to but not including 84th Streets. The view also shows 1-17 East 83rd Street, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Fifth Ave. No. 3 East 83rd Street, is a 2-story frame house.
March 14, 1925.
American Photo Service Inc.
